Retrieve the 1000 Genomes data, processed for tryptase allele counts

tryptase_1KG.Rd

See the background vignette of TrypLik for additional details.

Usage

tryptase_1KG()

Value

A data.frame of 2A/D, 2B/D, and the inferred genotype group for the 503 relevant samples

Examples

head(tryptase_1KG())
#>   2A/D   2B/D Geno Group
#> 1    0 2.9885      0α:4β
#> 2    0 3.2629      0α:4β
#> 3    0 3.4384      0α:4β
#> 4    0 3.4791      0α:4β
#> 5    0 3.4792      0α:4β
#> 6    0 3.5294      0α:4β
